commit.title: Create WARNERROR variable that controls the -warn-error flag for OCaml
commit.message:
Create WARNERROR variable that controls the -warn-error flag for OCaml
and the Sphinx "treat errors as warnings" flag (-W).  "1" enables these
flags, other values or undefined omit them.

Removed the "-warn-error" parameter to configure.  "-profile XXX" will
no longer cause these flags to be used.
